column5: any input on trout lake or these outfits? thanks

3rd year going with Boois. Used to go with a group that had been there for 15+ years. Boois will treat you very well, and you will be fishing out of 18' boats, which is a HUGE bonus on that body of water. 2 to a boat, unlike one other resort on the lake where I have seen 3 in a 16' boat.
